<p>I'm really sick and tired of all the razzmatazz about Fast Food joints out-doing each other with outrageous and calorie-excessive offerings. Not to mention the silly cliche of "a coronary on a bun" and the like. It's business. Like always. Not my choice, but I'm guessing a lot of people like this stuff. Oh, and thanks, Mr. Zim for clueing readers in on what Super Size Me was about. Had no idea!</p>
